# TDD GREEN PHASE SKILL

## Goal
Make a failing test pass using the smallest possible implementation.

---

## Input
- A failing test

---

## Output
- Minimal production code that makes the test pass

---

## Rules
- Write production code only
- Do not modify tests
- Do not refactor
- Do not introduce additional behavior

---

## Constraints
- Implementation must satisfy the current test only
- No speculative or future-proof code
- Stop immediately once the test passes